dbook is a collection of programs to manage a large book collection.

Features will include:
 * ISBN checker (Done)
 * ISBN Converter (Done)
 * Amazon book information retrieval (35%)
 * BibTeX output. (Done)
 * Book database management system

It consists out of libdbook with supplies all the necessary methods and different wrappers.

Wrappers:
 * Python
 * Java  
